# Screen Time Tracker for Opera
A simple browser extension that helps you track how much time you spend on different websites.

## Features
- Tracks time per website.
- Detects idle time and pauses tracking.
- Stores all data locally (no servers, no tracking).

## Installation (for developers)
1. Clone or download this repository.
2. Open Opera â†’ `opera://extensions`
3. Enable Developer Mode and click "Load unpacked".
4. Select this folder.

